      • getOrCreateParsedAnnexLibrary

        public static <T> T getOrCreateParsedAnnexLibrary(AadlPackage pkg,
                                                  java.lang.String annexName,
                                                  EClass parsedEType,
                                                  java.lang.Class<T> parsedType)
        Finds and returns the parsed annex library for the first annex library in the package with the specified name. Creates a new annex library if one does not exist. An exception is thrown if an existing annex library is found but it does not have a parsed annex library of the expected type.
        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of the parsed annex library
        Parameters:
        pkg - is the package in which to look for the annex library
        annexName - is the name of the annex library to look for
        parsedEType - is the EClass of the parsed annex library created if it the annex library doesn't exist.
        parsedType - is the java type that the parsed library is expected to be an instance of.
        Returns:
        the parsed annex library

        Finds and returns the parsed annex library for the first annex library in the package with the specified name. An exception is thrown if an annex library is found and it has a parsed annex library which is not an instance of the expected type.

        Parameters:

        parsedEType - is the EClass of the parsed annex subclause created if the annex subclause doesn't exist.
        parsedType - is the java type that the parsed subclause is expected to be an instance of.
        Returns:
        the parsed annex subclause
